dcterms:description: A dataset containing chest CT scans used for training convolutional neural networks to predict quality metrics for C-arm CBCT source trajectories.
dcterms:title: TCIA chest dataset

dcterms:description: A simulated dataset based on a semianthropomorphic representation of a human chest, generated to create projection data for training neural networks.
dcterms:title: Simulated dataset based on a semianthropomorphic representation of a human chest
